StrigelCMS is a flexible, but still simple and easy to use Content-Management-System.

It includes TinyMCE for easy creation of sites by people who don't have any HTML or CSS knownledge.
If you're familiar with PHP you can write your own modules to include your scripts and applications.

StrigelCMS features an event-based plugin system which allows you to customise the system to your needs.

Templates allow you to apply your own design to the website.